<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <head>
        <title>Movie Watchlist</title>
    </head>

    <body>

        <h1>🎬 Movie Watchlist App</h1>

        <p>
        Welcome! This app helps you keep track of movies you love (or hate 😏).
        </p>

        <hr>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>What you can do:</h2>

            <ul>
                <li>📌 Browse a list of movies</li>
                <li>⭐ Rate movies</li>
                <li>💬 Leave multiple comments on movies</li>
                <li>📂 Add movies to your personal watchlist</li>
                <li>📊 See average ratings for each movie</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <hr>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Get Started:</h2>

            <a href="/register" class="btn">Create an account</a>
            <a href="/login" class="btn">Login</a>
            <a href="/movie" class="btn">Browse Movies</a>
        </div>

    </body>
</html>